headline: LKQ Corporation to Release First Quarter 2025 Results on Thursday, April 24, 2025
summary: ANTIOCH, Tenn., March 27, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- LKQ Corporation (Nasdaq: LKQ) will release its first quarter 2025 financial results on Thursday, April 24, 2025. Conference Call Details LKQ will host a conference call and webcast on April 24, 2025 at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time (7:00 a.m. Central Time) with members of senior management to discuss the Company's results. To access the investor conference call, please dial (833) 470-1428. International access to the call may be obtained by dialing (40
